Advertising the requirements through various sources.
We need to shortlist the candidates based on the needs.
Shoot a mail to the selected candidate.
We are requesting the candidate to fill the Google form.
Notification will be sent to the interviewer on the candidates who have filled the Google form.
Now the interviewer will shortlist the candidate based on the response which they received.
Once again the interviewer will send a mail to the selected candidates.
This time instead of filling up the google form the candidates are requested to fill the survey.
